                            All announcements related to the conference are posted to the <a class="text-blue-600 no-underline" href="https://mail.python.org/mailman3/lists/inpycon-announce.python.org/" target="_blank">PyCon India Announce mailing list</a>. 
                            If you would like to volunteer, and contribute to the organization of PyCon India, join the <a class="text-blue-600 no-underline" href="https://mail.python.org/mailman/listinfo/inpycon" target="_blank">InPyCon mailing list</a>. 
                            We also have a presence on social media. All our announcements are posted on our 
                            <a class="text-blue-600 no-underline" href="https://x.com/pyconindia" target="_blank">X</a>, 
