                {% call renderDropdown("I am a first-time speaker & need some help in getting started. What should I do?") -%}
                    <div class="pt-4 px-4 text-lg">
                        <p> 
                            Check out the 
                            <a class="text-blue-600 no-underline" href="https://github.com/pythonindia/junction/wiki/Speaker-best-practices">Speaker best practices</a> to understand more about the process. 
                            For any doubts, feel free to reach out to us!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                {%- endcall %}
            </div>
            <div class="pt-4 text-[#000000] lg:pr-0">
                {% call renderDropdown("I want to volunteer for the conference. What should I do?") -%}
                    <div class="pt-4 px-4 text-lg">
                        <p> 
                            You can fill out the 
                            <a class="text-blue-600 no-underline" href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdX2LEom11BbWDiLUiQp1rmeNX9l7J8bfszGidsRDoExy0D5A/viewform" target="_blank">Volunteer Form</a> to understand more about the process. 
                            and subscribe to the <a class="text-blue-600 no-underline" href="https://mail.python.org/mailman/listinfo/inpycon" target="_blank">InPyCon mailing list</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                {%- endcall %}
            </div>
            <div class="pt-4 text-[#000000] lg:pr-0">
                {% call renderDropdown("Will the Internet and WiFi setup be good enough for a large crowd? Should I get a data card?") -%}
                    <div class="pt-4 px-4 text-lg">
                        <p class="font-bold">Workshops and Devsprints</p>
                        <p>
                            We try really hard to arrange good Internet at the venue. Most of the time it is adequate. 
                            However, the unpredictable amount of usage during these events sometimes causes problems. 
                            So it is fine if you don't carry a data card, but there is no harm in being prepared for the worst. 
                        </p>
                        <p class="font-bold">Conference</p>
                        <p>
                            Please note that Internet and WiFi will not be provided for the Conference sessions. 
                        </p>
                    </div>
                {%- endcall %}
            </div>
            <div class="pt-4 text-[#000000] lg:pr-0">
                {% call renderDropdown("How can I get in touch for queries or discussions related to PyCon India?") -%}
